title: Nature (New Episode)
overview: For more than a quarter-century, Nature has brought the beauty and wonder of the natural world into American homes, becoming in the process the benchmark of natural history programs on American television. The series has won more than 600 honors from the television industry, the international wildlife film community, parent groups, and environmental organizations â€“ including 10 Emmy Awards, three Peabody Awards, and the first honor ever given to a program by the Sierra Club.
